  <summary>6/7/2006--Introduced.
Children's Gasoline Burn Prevention Act - Directs the Consumer Product Safety Commission (CPSC) to promulgate final child-resistance product safety standards for closures on portable gasoline containers intended for use by consumers.

Prescribes criteria for such standards.</summary>
